          	HPS enables you to find for your accomodation and make payment directly with no hustle or stress. Just enter your email to get notification on the HPS launch day.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    	<div class="col-md-4">
      	<div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading"><h3>About STCs</h3></div>
          <div class="panel-body">
          	We create excellent innovative and more user interactive engineering softwares with reduced development time and high efficiency. STABLE CORPS employs advanced programming techniques to ensure that your needs are met. We at STABLE CORPS are ever ready to enable you to meet your deadlines when it comes to engineering software development.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    	<div class="col-md-4">
      	<div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-heading"><h3>Contact.</h3></div>
          <div class="panel-body">
          	<p>(+233)-020X XXX XXXX</p>
          	<p>P.O.Box XXX Ghana</p>
          	<p>Kumasi-KNUST campus</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  
	<div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <br><br>
          <p class="pull-right"><a href="http://www.stablecorps.com" target="blank">stablecorps.com</a> &nbsp; Â©Copyright 2014 STCs-HPS<sup></sup></p>
        <br><br>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
